<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM10.9.3">
<l>ārmali yāḻi caṅkoṭu paṟṟi yāṟṟalai yāṟṟalmi kuttuk</l>
<l>kārmukil vaṇṇā kaṉcaṉai muṉṉam kaṭantaniṉ kaṭuntiṟal tāṉō</l>
<l>nēriḻai mātai nittilat tottai neṭuṅkaṭa lamutaṉai yāḷai</l>
<l>yāreḻil vaṇṇā vaṅkaiyil vaṭṭā mivaḷeṉak karutukiṉ ṟāyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Dark cloud-hued one, holding a conch and extremely sharp discus,</l>
<l>Why the cruel force that once overcame Kaṁsa, amplifying your strength</l>
<l rend="indent">[over his] strength?</l>
<l>Our lady with strung jewels, this cluster of pearls,</l>
<l rend="indent">the one like nectar churned from the sea,</l>
<l>You whose hue is full of beauty, you think that she is [just] a pawn</l>
<l rend="indent">in your fine hand.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
